                                                  Commentary on the Computus</title>
              <note>Commentary on the <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3851Hassab">We have written a
                                                  computus that we will remember in order not to
                                                  congregate with apostates...</ref></note>
              <textLang mainLang="am" otherLangs="gez">Amharic and Gǝʿǝz</textLang>
              <incipit>
                <foreign xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ንዌጥን፡ በረድኤተ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡
